Dialogue: 0,00:00:10.25,00:00:12.30,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（イタチ）日が昇ってから→
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.36,0:00:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been making us walk\Nquite a distance since sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:12.30,00:00:14.34,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ずいぶん歩かされてる。
Dialogue: 0,00:00:14.34,00:00:19.64,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いよいよ戦いのようだな。\N（長門）いったい　どいつらだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Our battle must be imminent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Who will we be fighting?
Dialogue: 0,00:00:25.14,00:00:28.27,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,まさかな…。\N近いのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.36,0:00:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they close?
Dialogue: 0,00:00:28.27,00:00:32.96,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もう懐かしく感じるな。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels familiar, nostalgic...
Dialogue: 0,00:00:37.99,00:00:40.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（ナルト）うちはイタチに…　長門！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.28,0:00:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi Uchiha... and Nagato!
Dialogue: 0,00:00:40.29,00:00:44.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（キラービー）知り合いか？　ナルト。\Nあぁ　２人ともな。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You know these guys, Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.20,0:00:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know both of them.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:44.21,00:00:49.79,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,まさか　お前と戦わされることに\Nなるとはな…　ナルト。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.45,0:00:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined I'd be forced\Ninto fighting you again, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:49.79,00:00:53.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,久しぶりに会ったことに\Nなるんだろうが→
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably been\Na while since we last met.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:53.52,00:00:56.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,死んでたんで　すぐな気もするな。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:00:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But since I've been dead, it feels\Nlike it's only been a moment.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:56.50,00:01:01.31,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,少し変わったな　ナルト。\Nあぁ　これか。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.49,0:01:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You've changed a bit, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean this?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:01.31,00:01:04.72,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,これってば\N九尾のチャクラをコントロールした→
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.49,0:01:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in control of\Nthe Nine Tails' chakra now.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:04.72,00:01:08.46,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,チャクラモードってやつだってばよ。\Nなに！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.03,0:01:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my Chakra Mode!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:08.46,00:01:12.55,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（長門）なるほど\Nだから変わって見えたのか。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.74,0:01:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.95,0:01:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...\NNo wonder you look different.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:12.55,00:01:14.86,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,顔つきが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.07,0:01:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your face.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:17.01,00:01:20.35,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,九尾の力を\Nコントロールしたというのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.36,0:01:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You now command\Nthe Power of the Nine Tails?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:20.35,00:01:22.72,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ここまで成長するとはな。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.49,0:01:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed with\Nyour development!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:22.72,00:01:27.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺の弟弟子だからな。\N思ったとおりだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.24,0:01:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He and I are sibling students.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.65,0:01:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not surprised!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:27.50,00:01:31.69,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それ　俺のおかげ。\Nそれまで結構　こいつは日陰。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.95,0:01:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,For that, it's me he owes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I came along, he was\Npretty much in the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:31.69,00:01:34.05,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そんなこともなかったってばよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so not true!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:34.05,00:01:38.87,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なら　憎しみを\N克服できたってことだな？　ナルト。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.95,0:01:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've overcome hatred, Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:38.87,00:01:43.27,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,おう！　兄弟分のあんたが\N教えてくれた痛み→
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.40,0:01:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! As my senior,\Nyou taught me about pain.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:43.27,00:01:46.35,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ビーのおっちゃんとの\N真実の滝での修業や→
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.57,0:01:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The training I did at the Waterfall\Nof Truth with Octopops...
Dialogue: 0,00:01:46.35,00:01:48.41,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,父ちゃんや母ちゃん。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.49,0:01:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom and dad...
Dialogue: 0,00:01:48.41,00:01:51.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,とにかく　みんなのおかげで\Nここまで来られた。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I have all of you to thank\Nfor where I am now!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:51.95,00:01:54.35,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そうか。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.74,0:01:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,00:01:54.35,00:01:58.05,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ナルト　お前に聞きたいことがある。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.07,0:01:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto, I must ask you...
Dialogue: 0,00:01:58.05,00:02:03.65,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ん？　そういや俺も　あんたに\N聞きたいことがあったんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.90,0:02:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question for you,\Nas well.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:06.08,00:02:09.60,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（カブト）どうやら僕が\N先に見つけたようだね。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like I found you first...\NEight Tails and Nine Tails.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:09.60,00:02:14.23,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,八尾と九尾\Nこの２枚のカードさえあれば→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,With these two cards,\Nhe'll fall right into my hands.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:14.23,00:02:17.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あいつも僕の言いなりだ。
Dialogue: 0,00:02:17.77,00:02:20.91,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《どんな顔して悔しがるのか→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Too bad I won't be able to see{\i0}\N{\i1}the frustrated look on{\i0}
