Dialogue: 0,00:04:14.06,00:04:17.98,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ナルト　お前に聞きたいことがある。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto, I must ask you...
Dialogue: 0,00:04:17.98,00:04:23.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ん？　そういや俺も　あんたに\N聞きたいことがあったんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question for you, as well.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:30.31,00:04:32.41,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヨウ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo?!
Dialogue: 0,00:04:39.73,00:04:43.08,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あれ？　熱かった？　怠慢　すまん。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, was that hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for not giving it all I got.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:43.08,00:04:45.42,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,鮫肌か…。
