Dialogue: 0,00:04:51.28,00:04:54.14,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,後ろで操ってるやつの言いなり。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's under a spell...
Dialogue: 0,00:04:54.14,00:04:58.83,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,タイミングなんて関係ない。　オーケー？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.82,0:04:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he cuts you off,\Nwhat the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:04:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
