Dialogue: 0,00:05:09.59,00:05:12.64,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,暁のメンバーに入っちまった！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He joined the Akatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:12.64,00:05:17.42,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なぜ　サスケは　里へ帰らない？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't Sasuke return\Nto the village?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:17.42,00:05:22.13,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あんたの　極秘任務のことを\N聞かされて…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He found out about\Nyour top-secret mission,
Dialogue: 0,00:05:22.13,00:05:25.43,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そんで　里を潰すことを\N選んだんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and chose to destroy the village!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:27.52,00:05:29.51,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,極秘任務？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Top-secret mission?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:29.51,00:05:31.51,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（イタチ）まさか　マダラが！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me Madara...?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:39.78,00:05:45.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺も　あんたの本当のことを\Nマダラから聞いた。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Madara told me the truth too.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:45.81,00:05:48.83,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そういうことか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was...
Dialogue: 0,00:05:48.83,00:05:52.89,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ってことは　マダラの言ったことは\Nやっぱ　本当だったんだな？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So Madara was telling the truth!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:52.89,00:05:55.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うちは一族が\N里を乗っ取ろうとして　それを…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Uchiha Clan tried to\Ntake over the village and...
Dialogue: 0,00:05:55.85,00:05:58.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もういい　ナルト。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You've said enough, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:58.47,00:06:01.16,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そうなのか？　イタチ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true, Itachi?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:01.16,00:06:05.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,イタチ　あんたは\N里とサスケを守るため→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You died playing the villain
Dialogue: 0,00:06:05.20,00:06:07.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,自分を　悪党に見せかけて死んだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to protect\Nthe village and Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:07.47,00:06:12.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あんたの苦しみも覚悟も\Nサスケは　理解しているはずだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke surely understands\Nyour pain and resolve!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:12.21,00:06:15.80,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,でも　サスケは　あんたの意志を\N受け継ぐどころか→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But instead of seeing\Nyour wishes through,
Dialogue: 0,00:06:15.80,00:06:18.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉を潰す気でいる。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke is trying to\Ndestroy the village.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:18.17,00:06:21.53,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それは　大好きだった兄貴を\N苦しめた里への→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is his way of avenging
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the pain the village caused\Nhis beloved older brother!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:21.53,00:06:24.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,弔い合戦のつもりなんだ。
Dialogue: 0,00:06:24.90,00:06:31.22,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《マダラめ…　俺のことを\Nやはり知っていたか》
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn Madara,{\i0}\N{\i1}he knew the truth about me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:06:31.22,00:06:35.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そのことを　里の皆は\Nもう知っているのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do the villagers know about this?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:35.21,00:06:38.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,カカシ先生と　ヤマト隊長は\N一緒にいたから…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.49,0:06:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi Sensei and\NCaptain Yamato were there too.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:38.85,00:06:42.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,でも　マダラの言ったことは\N確証もねえから→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was nothing to prove\Nwhat Madara said,
Dialogue: 0,00:06:42.29,00:06:44.18,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,カカシ先生に　口止めされている。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so Kakashi Sensei is keeping\Neveryone tight-lipped.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:44.18,00:06:46.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,他は　誰も知らねえと思う。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think anyone else knows.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:46.90,00:06:51.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なら　このことは\N里の皆には　決して言うな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then don't ever tell\Nthe village about this!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:51.29,00:06:55.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,名誉ある　うちは一族に\N変わりはないのだからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't let the Uchiha Clan's\Nreputation change!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:55.52,00:06:57.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それと…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And one more thing...
Dialogue: 0,00:06:57.52,00:07:00.22,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《クソ！　体が勝手に！》
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.53,0:07:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn! My body is moving{\i0}\N{\i1}on its own!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:07:00.22,00:07:02.23,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,万象天引！\Nうわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Universal Pull!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:13.27,00:07:15.34,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,よく　かわしたぞ　ナルト。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nicely dodged, Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:15.34,00:07:18.64,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ペインと　やり合った時よりは\N強くなってっからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stronger now than\Nwhen Pain and I fought.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:25.93,00:07:28.57,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,サスケは　お前に任せる。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you deal with Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:28.57,00:07:30.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,はなっから　そのつもりだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my plan from the start!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:30.97,00:07:34.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,やはり　お前に託して正解だった。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Entrusting it to you was\Nthe right thing to do, after all.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:37.00,00:07:39.34,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,よし　ナルト　まず俺を引き離せ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Naruto, pull me away!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:39.34,00:07:41.94,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺には　機動力がない。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't move by myself.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:44.23,00:07:46.67,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,口寄せの術！\Nえっ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Summoning Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:53.25,00:07:55.30,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（長門）こともないか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe I can...
Dialogue: 0,00:07:55.30,00:07:57.92,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あんた　そんなキャラだったか～！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:07:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you always do that?
Dialogue: 0,00:07:57.92,00:07:59.91,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,後ろだ！
Dialogue: 0,00:07:59.91,00:08:02.32,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,わかってる　オーケー！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:02.32,00:08:04.92,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《火遁　鳳仙花爪紅》
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fire Style! Phoenix Flower Jutsu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:08:13.71,00:08:15.71,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あちちち…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot! Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:23.66,00:08:26.96,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,捕まえたぜ！　バカ野郎　この野郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Caught you! Ya fool, ya fool!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:34.00,00:08:37.99,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヘッ！　図体がでけえわりには\Nあっけなかったってばよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,For someone so big,\Nthat was easy!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:37.99,00:08:40.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,油断するな　ナルト！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your guard up, Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:46.30,00:08:49.69,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ゲッ！　ゲェ！\Nなんだってばよ！？　これ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:59.66,00:09:02.07,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《幻術！》
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Genjutsu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:09:02.07,00:09:05.07,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺の眼を　直接　見るな。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,00:09:09.07,00:09:12.07,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いてっ！\N（八尾）目を覚ませ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,00:09:14.69,00:09:17.05,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ウィ～！　鮫肌！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Samehada!
Dialogue: 0,00:09:32.76,00:09:37.37,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,八尾がサビのキラービーだぜ\N俺様が。　アッ　イェ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Killer Bee the Eight Tails!\NThat's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:03.21,00:10:06.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,きりがねえ。\Nそいつを殴ると増える。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This'll go on forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He multiplies every time\Nyou hit him!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:06.81,00:10:09.42,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いったん俺を倒せ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock me down first!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:19.36,00:10:22.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ビーのおっちゃん　気をつけろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch yourself, Octopops!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:22.36,00:10:25.40,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,天照も月読も\Nくらったら終わりだぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get struck by Amaterasu or\NTsukuyomi, it'll be the end of you!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:25.40,00:10:27.70,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,万華鏡写輪眼だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got the Mangekyo Sharingan!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:31.16,00:10:34.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ウッ…。
Dialogue: 0,00:10:40.36,00:10:43.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ウッ…。
Dialogue: 0,00:10:48.97,00:10:53.70,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ウッ…。
Dialogue: 0,00:10:53.70,00:10:56.60,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,カァ～ッ。\Nやはり出たか。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's out.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:59.68,00:11:02.68,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《瞳力でナルトに何かしたのか？》
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did he do something to Naruto{\i0}\N{\i1}with his Visual Prowess?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:11:02.68,00:11:05.62,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ウッ…。
Dialogue: 0,00:11:05.62,00:11:08.65,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,カァ～ッ。\Nゲホッ　ゲホッ。
Dialogue: 0,00:11:08.65,00:11:13.55,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なんで　俺の口から\Nカラスが出てくるんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did a crow\Ncome out of my mouth?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:19.45,00:11:22.42,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((なぜ　そこまで弟にこだわる？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are you so attached{\i0}\N{\i1}to my brother?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:11:22.42,00:11:26.08,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あいつは　抜け忍だろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.36,0:11:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's a Rogue Ninja.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:11:26.08,00:11:28.79,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,少なくともお前なんかより→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's because unlike you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:11:28.79,00:11:32.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あいつのことを\N兄弟だと思っているからだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.03,0:11:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think of him as a brother,{\i0}\N{\i1}more than you ever did.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:11:41.93,00:11:44.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,カァ～ッ　カァ～ッ。
Dialogue: 0,00:11:44.90,00:11:48.09,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（イタチ）お前はすでに幻術の中だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're already under my genjutsu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:11:48.09,00:11:50.39,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,クソッ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:11:53.24,00:11:58.06,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もう一度言う。\Nお前と少し話がしたいだけだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll say it again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just wanted to talk to you{\i0}\N{\i1}for a moment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:11:58.06,00:12:03.02,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前はサスケを\N連れ戻したがっていたな。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've been trying to take{\i0}\N{\i1}Sasuke back to the village.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:03.02,00:12:06.03,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だが　うまくいかなかったら\Nどうする？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But what if it doesn't go{\i0}\N{\i1}the way you want?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:06.03,00:12:09.13,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どうやってでも連れ戻す。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll do anything to make it happen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:09.13,00:12:12.04,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,無理やりにでもか。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even by force?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:12.04,00:12:16.12,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,運よくサスケが　おとなしく\N里に帰れば　確かにそれでいいが→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If, by some turn of luck,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke goes with you{\i0}\N{\i1}willingly, great.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:16.12,00:12:19.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それとまったく逆の場合は\Nどうする？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But what if the exact{\i0}\N{\i1}opposite happens?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:19.84,00:12:23.73,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What does that mean?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:23.73,00:12:29.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,さっきお前は\Nサスケを兄弟のようだと言ったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You just said you consider{\i0}\N{\i1}Sasuke to be like a brother...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:29.21,00:12:32.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ならば　もし　そのサスケが\N木ノ葉を襲ってきたら→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What if Sasuke were to attack{\i0}\N{\i1}the Leaf Village?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:32.95,00:12:37.34,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どうすると聞いているんだ。\Nなんだ？　なんでサスケが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would you do then?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?{\i0}\N{\i1}Why would Sasuke...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:37.34,00:12:39.93,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そんなことするわけねえだろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way he'd do{\i0}\N{\i1}something like that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:39.93,00:12:42.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,サスケは　まだ純粋だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke is still naïve.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:42.84,00:12:45.74,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,簡単に何色にでも染まる。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He can easily be dyed any color.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:45.74,00:12:49.98,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そうなった場合\Nお前はやつを止められるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In such a case,{\i0}\N{\i1}can you stop him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:49.98,00:12:53.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(サスケを殺してでも))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you have to kill Sasuke?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:53.97,00:12:57.08,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そういや　あのとき…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.45,0:12:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, back then...
Dialogue: 0,00:13:00.62,00:13:03.59,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((うぐっ…。
Dialogue: 0,00:13:03.59,00:13:07.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（イタチ）\Nお前に俺の力を分けてやった。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have shared some of{\i0}\N{\i1}my power with you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:13:07.84,00:13:12.44,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(その力…\N使う日が来なければいいがな))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Though I hope the day never comes{\i0}\N{\i1}when you'll have to use it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:13:15.13,00:13:17.44,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《この感じ…》
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This feeling!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:13:19.64,00:13:22.28,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ナルト　天照だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto! It's Amaterasu!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:22.28,00:13:24.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,くっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:13:24.47,00:13:27.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,神羅天征！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Almighty Push!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:27.36,00:13:29.66,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,クソッ！　また勝手に。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! My body's moving\Nby itself again!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:33.15,00:13:36.61,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なんだ！？　どういうことだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:46.28,00:13:49.28,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,天照じゃないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not Amaterasu?
Dialogue: 0,00:13:56.33,00:13:59.22,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,こうなったか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:13:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is...
Dialogue: 0,00:13:59.22,00:14:01.38,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どうなったんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How what is...?
Dialogue: 0,00:14:01.38,00:14:03.68,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,天照！\Nえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Amaterasu...
Dialogue: 0,00:14:13.23,00:14:16.24,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,天照を外した？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He used Amaterasu?
Dialogue: 0,00:14:20.51,00:14:23.24,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あのカラス　お前のだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That crow... It's yours, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,00:14:23.24,00:14:25.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あのカラスで何をしたんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do with that crow?
Dialogue: 0,00:14:28.50,00:14:30.88,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（カブト）侮っていた。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I underestimated him...
Dialogue: 0,00:14:30.88,00:14:36.55,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うちはイタチ…　こいつは\N普通のやつとは明らかに違う。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi Uchiha.\NHe's clearly different from the rest.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:36.55,00:14:39.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,この穢土転生の術まで…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He resisted my Reanimation Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:39.85,00:14:45.33,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うまくいった。\Nあぁ　そういうことか。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so that's it...
Dialogue: 0,00:14:45.33,00:14:47.33,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,天照！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Amaterasu!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:00.21,00:15:02.25,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,来た！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:02.25,00:15:06.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,落ち着け。\Nもう俺は操られてはいない。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no longer being controlled.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:06.21,00:15:09.24,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,この敵の術の上に\N新たな幻術をかけた。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I used a new genjutsu against\Nthe enemy's jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:09.24,00:15:14.59,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,え？\N「木ノ葉の里を守れ」という幻術だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.36,0:15:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A genjutsu that orders me\Nto protect the Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:14.59,00:15:18.55,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,よって\N穢土転生の術は打ち消された。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.86,0:15:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It erased the Reanimation Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:18.55,00:15:22.60,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そのカラスは　俺の万華鏡写輪眼に→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I prepared that crow to respond\Nto my Mangekyo Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:22.60,00:15:25.61,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,呼応して出てくるように\N細工しておいたものだ。
Dialogue: 0,00:15:25.61,00:15:28.60,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もしもの時のためにな。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in case, for times like this.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:28.60,00:15:30.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:30.77,00:15:34.73,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,カラスの左眼に仕込んでおいたのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's implanted in that crow's left eye.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:34.73,00:15:37.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,やつの眼だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}his{\i0} eye!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:37.77,00:15:41.58,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,こんなことができる幻術は\Nひとつしかない。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.61,0:15:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one genjutsu\Nthat can do that.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:41.58,00:15:44.28,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うちはシスイ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Shisui Uchiha's...
Dialogue: 0,00:15:44.28,00:15:46.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,万華鏡写輪眼。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The ultimate Mangekyo Sharingan\Ngenjutsu in existence:
Dialogue: 0,00:15:46.47,00:15:50.27,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,最強幻術　別天神！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Koto Amatsukami.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:54.12,00:15:57.62,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,その幻術で　俺は元に戻った。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Using that genjutsu,\NI was able to restore myself.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:57.62,00:16:01.58,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どうやら　シスイの万華鏡は\N切られたようだが。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears Shisui's Mangekyo\Nhad already worn off, though.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:01.58,00:16:04.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うちはシスイ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shisui Uchiha?
Dialogue: 0,00:16:04.47,00:16:09.46,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うちは最強の幻術使い\N瞬身のシスイか。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Uchiha's most powerful\Ngenjutsu user....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shisui the Teleporter?
Dialogue: 0,00:16:09.46,00:16:14.31,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,シスイの瞳力は\N対象者が幻術にかけられたと→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shisui's Visual Prowess creates\Na powerful genjutsu
Dialogue: 0,00:16:14.31,00:16:18.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,自覚することなく\N操ることができる最強幻術を生む。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,that allows you to control someone\Nwithout them ever realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:18.82,00:16:22.96,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,「木ノ葉を守れ」という幻術を\Nシスイの眼に仕込み→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I programmed the genjutsu,\Nto protect the Leaf, into Shisui's eye.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:22.96,00:16:29.34,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,その眼をカラスの左眼に埋め込んで\Nお前に渡しておいたのだ　ナルト。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I put it into the crow's left eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and after that,\NI gave the crow to you, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:29.34,00:16:34.48,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,まさか　自分自身にかけることに\Nなるとは思わなかったがな。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I never realized that I'd be\Nusing it on myself someday.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:34.48,00:16:39.79,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なんで　その眼を　あんたが持って\N俺なんかに渡したんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you have that eye,\Nand why did you give it to me?
Dialogue: 0,00:16:42.97,00:16:47.79,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,自己犠牲…\N陰から平和を支える名もなき忍。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-sacrifice...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The mark of a true shinobi is\Nthat they do not seek glory.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:47.79,00:16:50.63,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それが本当の忍。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They protect from the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:50.63,00:16:54.02,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,シスイが俺に教えてくれたものだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shisui taught me that.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:54.02,00:16:59.41,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,シスイは　己の眼を巡って　やがて\N争いが起きることを予感し→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:17:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shisui anticipated that a battle\Nwould ensue for his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:59.41,00:17:02.70,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,その眼とともに\N死んだように見せかけた。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He faked his own death
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and made it seem like\Nhis eyes were destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:02.70,00:17:06.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺も里の疑惑を受けることで\Nその手伝いをした。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I helped him by becoming\Nthe target of suspicion in the village.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:06.85,00:17:13.86,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,最後にシスイと会った時\N右眼はダンゾウに奪われたあとだった。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.24,0:17:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When I last saw Shisui,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Danzo had managed to\Nsteal his right eye.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:13.86,00:17:16.33,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だが　残った左眼を→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He bequeathed his remaining\Nleft eye to me,
Dialogue: 0,00:17:16.33,00:17:20.41,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,里を守るために使えと\N俺に託し　やつは消えた。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,telling me to use it to protect\Nthe village, and disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:20.41,00:17:23.05,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺は　その眼を→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave that eye to you,\Nbecause you share Shisui's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:23.05,00:17:27.34,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,シスイと同じ気持を持っていた\Nお前に渡した。
Dialogue: 0,00:17:27.34,00:17:31.78,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺の残したサスケが\N里の脅威になったのだとしたら→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If Sasuke, whom I left behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,ever became a threat\Nto the village...
Dialogue: 0,00:17:31.78,00:17:36.40,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,眼を預かった者として\Nシスイの気持に反したことになる。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,then I would have violated all\Nthat Shisui entrusted me to do.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:36.40,00:17:41.03,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それを正すことができる者は\Nお前しかいなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the only one\Nwho can make it right.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:41.03,00:17:44.40,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前は　サスケを兄弟だと言った。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.11,0:17:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you consider\NSasuke a brother.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:44.40,00:17:47.38,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だからこそ\Nサスケを止められるのは→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I felt that you, Naruto,
Dialogue: 0,00:17:47.38,00:17:50.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ナルト　お前だけだと思った。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,were the only one\Nwho could stop him.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:50.90,00:17:55.44,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,本当の力…\N永遠の万華鏡を手にするために→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,True power...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In his quest for\Nthe Eternal Mangekyo,
Dialogue: 0,00:17:55.44,00:17:59.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,サスケは\N俺の眼を移植するとふんでいた。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke planned on transplanting\Nmy eyes into himself.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:59.20,00:18:02.93,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そうなったとき\N移植した俺の眼に呼応して→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If that ever happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that crow was supposed\Nto emerge from you,
Dialogue: 0,00:18:02.93,00:18:08.05,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前からカラスが現れ\Nサスケに　別天神をかける。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,in response to your coming into\Ncontact with my transplanted eyes,
Dialogue: 0,00:18:08.05,00:18:10.59,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,「木ノ葉を守れ」と…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and cast the Koto Amatsukami\Nto protect the Leaf, onto Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:10.59,00:18:13.61,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そういう手筈だった。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my plan.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:13.61,00:18:18.56,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なぜ　シスイの眼で　初めから\Nサスケに　その術をしなかった？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you cast that jutsu\Non Sasuke from the start,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,using Shisui's eye?
Dialogue: 0,00:18:18.56,00:18:24.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,しなかったんじゃない\Nできなかったからだ…　当時はな。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I didn't, I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at that time...
Dialogue: 0,00:18:24.95,00:18:29.91,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,シスイの万華鏡は\N再発動まで十数年かかる。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shisui's Mangekyo would take\Ndecades to reactivate,
Dialogue: 0,00:18:29.91,00:18:33.62,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,千住柱間のチャクラでもないかぎりな。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,unless you had\NHashirama Senju's chakra.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:33.62,00:18:37.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それに\Nサスケには　俺の死を利用して→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, there were many things
Dialogue: 0,00:18:37.29,00:18:41.43,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いろいろと\Nしてやりたいことがあった。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke wanted to\Nuse my death for.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:41.43,00:18:45.98,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,イタチ…　信頼してくれてありがとう。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for trusting me.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:45.98,00:18:49.42,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もう心配ばかりしなくていい。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:49.42,00:18:54.59,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あんたは里のために\N十分すぎるほどやったじゃねえか。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done more than\Nenough for the village.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:54.59,00:18:57.60,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あとは　俺に任せてくれ。
